##-----------------------DIE---------------------##
group Die

anim DieUp 
frametime 200
repeat false
key die_right_1
key die_right_2
key die_right_3
key die_right_4
endkey 

anim DieDown
frametime 200
repeat false
key die_left_1
key die_left_2
key die_left_3
key die_left_4
endkey 

